label: latestReceivedGeographicalCoordinate
comment: The latest geographical coordinates received by this monitoring IOT device, from the perspective of the receiver.

rangeIncludes.comment: A set of geographical coordinates of a specific point such as the longitude, latitude and altitude.

domainIncludes.comment: An object or system made or adapted for an IOT (Internet of Things) purpose such as to collect, report and autonomously transmit digital data especially when connected to a piece of mechanical or electronic equipment.
